This package bundles tokenizer assets derived from official Hugging Face repositories under the BSC-LT organization:
- BSC-LT/salamandra-7b tokenizer.json
- BSC-LT/salamandra-7b-instruct tokenizer.json

This package also registers the following official BSC-LT models that share those tokenizer families:
- BSC-LT/salamandra-2b
- BSC-LT/salamandra-2b-instruct
- BSC-LT/ALIA-40b
- BSC-LT/ALIA-40b-instruct-2601

